{
  "stem": "12882.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I played with the Orchestra of the Mozart [GERMAN], and so on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And to put that in perspective is that 1933, my solo career was already finished because Hitler came into power and I had to restrict my playing to a Jewish organization.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My brother followed suit.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "When he was six years old, he started to play the piano, in a different way than I did.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My brother always did only what he liked to do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the rest, you could stand on your head, he didn't show any interest and let it go.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a young brother, two years younger.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name was Fritz Joachim Meyer, F-R-I-T-Z, Joachim, J-O-A-C-H-I-M.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From this moment on, my mother had a hard time to come close to the piano again, because he dominated.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was-- I am not a good judge, but I think he was the greater of the two talents of us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had plenty of talents.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It went very fast.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I know that, after about a year at the conservatory-- the young violin teacher was a lovely man by the name of Slovinsky, S-L-O-V-I-N-S-K-Y-- gave me a copy of the Bach Solo Sonatas and Partitas, and said, I'm sure you will play them one day, and you'll play them well, but I cannot teach you anything anymore.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You need a better teacher.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, I have been a teacher for nearly 50 years.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I have never heard such an understatement from anybody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Anyway, my father saw to it that I got another very good teacher.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my parents always saw to it that we got the best there could be.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "For instance, every Sunday, my father had to go and wind up the light clocks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So in the evening, the light would go on in the display windows.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
